    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7, then boil half a kettle</p><p>Rinse your<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat, once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain, return it to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/doner-style-falafel-rice-bowl-with-garlicky-feta-yoghurt/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot </strong>finely</p><p>Add your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong> and <strong>sliced shallot </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>cider vinegar</strong>, 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[85ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside to pickle \u2013 this is your <strong>quick-pickled red cabbage</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/doner-style-falafel-rice-bowl-with-garlicky-feta-yoghurt/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>falafel </strong>to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 5-8 min or until browned and warmed though</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/doner-style-falafel-rice-bowl-with-garlicky-feta-yoghurt/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways and scrape out the inner seeds with a teaspoon</p><p>Roughly chop the <strong>inner seeds</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>deseeded cucumber</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>in half, then slice finely</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/doner-style-falafel-rice-bowl-with-garlicky-feta-yoghurt/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Crumble your <strong>feta </strong>finely</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/doner-style-falafel-rice-bowl-with-garlicky-feta-yoghurt/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>crumbled feta</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>chopped cucumber seeds</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and stir to combine \u2013 this is your <strong>feta cheese garlic yoghurt</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/doner-style-falafel-rice-bowl-with-garlicky-feta-yoghurt/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>To build your rice bowl, serve the <strong>cooked rice</strong> in a bowl and top with the <strong>cooked falafel</strong>, <strong>sliced cucumber</strong>, <strong>sliced tomato</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled red cabbage</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>doner-style falafel brown rice bowl</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/doner-style-falafel-rice-bowl-with-garlicky-feta-yoghurt/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>falafel brown rice bowl </strong>and drizzle with the <strong>feta garlic yoghurt</strong> and your <strong>sriracha </strong>over the top</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
